verbose_text: Importantly, we show that constitutive absence of TYROBP / DAP12 in the amyloidosis mouse model prevented appearance of the electrophysiological and learning behavior alterations associated with the phenotype of APP KM670/671NL / PSEN1 Deltaexon9 mice.
